      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, naturally aspirated with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure VANOS. This example is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, delivering power to the rear wheels via a 3.62 ratio limited-slip differential. To address common chassis concerns, the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates, and the rod bearings have been serviced to ensure long-term mechanical sympatico. The suspension features a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup with refreshed bushings for sharp turn-in and lateral stability. While the exterior shows honest patina from spirited use, the mechanical vitals are robust, offering a visceral analog experience for the purist.",
