    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2017 Porsche Macan S in Volcano Grey Metallic. This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between a refined daily driver and a high-performance SUV. The exterior retains a deep, glossy luster, showing only minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the Agate Grey leather interior remains supple and clean, with very minimal bolster wear on the power-adjustable seats. Every feature\u2014from the expansive panoramic sunroof to the crisp Bose surround sound system\u2014functions exactly as it should. Mechanically, this Macan is in robust health; it comes with a documented service history, including a recent full synthetic oil change and a brake system inspection. The 3.0L Twin-Turbo V6 delivers smooth, responsive power, while the PDK transmission provides the sharp, seamless shifts Porsche is known for. It rides on 20-inch RS Spyder Design wheels with tires that offer excellent tread depth. This is a reliable, turn-key luxury vehicle that has been treated with respect and is ready for its next chapter.",
